{"name": "CREATIVE GROUP ECONOMICS", "image": "", "description": "At Creative Group Economics, we believe that breaking out of poverty begins with spending your own dollars in your own community. Our goal is to change the mindsets of our people, and be the kinds of leaders that we hope to be and an echo the morals required to take on our communities biggest problems. It starts by standing with those who support you, listening to voices unheard, and recognizing potential where others see despair.  \u201cIt demands investing as a means, not an end, daring to go where markets have failed and aid has fallen short.\u201d It makes our capital work for us, not control us. {"name": "MOTHERLAND COOKING XPERIENCE", "image": "https://officialblackwallstreet.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/CoverMCX13cover3-823x420.jpg", "description": "We take you on an exciting cultural and educational journey to Africa through cooking experiences paired with live African music, drinks and storytelling. Learn how to cook delicious dishes from the continent of Africa either in person or online.
Motherland Cooking Xperience was founded with the aim of providing a platform for immigrants with ties to Africa to showcase their talent, through food, music, art, and storytelling in an effort to bridge the cultural gap between African immigrants, their families and their communities of residence.
We also want to empower them financially and foster faster inclusion and participation in their communities. At Motherland Cooking Xperience, we are passionate about teaching cultural competency by showcasing the diverse and exciting cultures of Africa through interactive delicious cooking demos and classes, beverages and food, as well as music and storytelling from Africa.
We are a practical option for improving and increasing cultural competency for schools, companies and the community as a whole.
Website: https://www.motherlandcookingxperience.com
Social media handles:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xperienceafricancooking
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/motherlandcookingxperience
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNOBBqAvOuEOh3oE5wDfP4w
Why do you need our products/services?
Every cooking experience is a hands-on but relaxed experience.
Plus, we are excited that you get to go home with the easy to follow recipes straight from our homes to yours.
– We can travel to you
– Learn about Africa’s diversity and cultures
– Travel without ever living your home.
– We offer a safe space to ask questions
– It is fun and relaxing
– Cook in your kitchen and be as free as a bird
– Increase your cultural intelligence
– Your kids will become world citizens and hone their cooking skills
– Reconnect with the motherland even before you get there
– Continue re-connection after visiting or tracing roots
– If you want to host this experience at your home with friends and families, we got you!
– If this is for team building for your employees or cultural competency training, we got you!
– Are you looking for a new cultural experience? We got you!
– Are you trying to trace and reconnect with your roots back in the motherland? We got you.
– Bachelorette parties, Girls Night Out, Foodies and Adventurers, we got you!
– If you need culturally competent experiences that transform your kids to world citizens, we got you!
Our Services:
1. Annual Pass Our annual virtual subscription comes with:
a. 1 Download of 10 African Recipes worth $10
b. 1 annual admission to 12 Virtual Motherland Cooking Xperience events with an African chef and live music worth $420 ($35 per month.)
c. Live African Music from diverse talented African musicians.
d. Learn about ingredients used and the regions or countries they come from. Full values at $427.69, you only pay $199.79 and save $227.9
Link: https://www.motherlandcookingxperience.com/product-page/annual-motherland-cooking-xperience-membership
2. Kids Cooking Classes
Welcome to Motherland Cooking Xperience, the only fully curated African cultural experience that pairs food, art, storytelling, and music together in a unique, interactive, and intimate setting.
Are you looking for something educational, special, ethnic; an adventurous experience for you and your kids?
We have got you!
Join us this year for the perfect mix of cooking, eating, and food-themed fun. In these 2-hour camps, kids get to chop, blend, and cook their way to a different delicious dish from Africa each day. We will; enjoy our creations together at the end with plenty left for the whole family!
Each day includes about an hour of cooking (with you acting as your child’s sous chef as needed), along with education about the ingredients, the people that use them, and their region of origin in Africa.
Interactive and engaging with small camp sizes on Zoom platform (max 12 participants/screens)
Delicious vegetarian recipes with modifications are available for allergies/dietary restrictions. Recipes, ingredient list & equipment list provided in advance.
We are excited to share these recipes and stories with you. Our cooks are seasoned cooks from different African countries, each one bringing their own style, stories, and history with love.
So, come away with us to Africa!
What you get: 1 recipe per class Live music Storytelling Discover Africa
Further instructions: The price is $125 per week. Monday-Friday 9:30-11:30 am (US Central time) Siblings or family members in the same household can participate on a shared screen (provided they are within the age range or older). Camps are nonrefundable, and we regret we can’t offer makeups for missed days.
Meal Prep Kit Add-on: $100 (Greater Grand Rapids Only) https://www.motherlandcookingxperience.com/product-page/kids-cooking-classes
3. Date Night
It’s Date Night; let us take you to Africa. You will be guided by our chef and serenaded by our African creative.
Welcome to Motherland Cooking Xperience, the only fully curated African cultural experience that pairs food, art storytelling, and music together in a unique, interactive and virtual setting. We are excited to share these recipes and stories with you. Our cooks are seasoned cooks from different African countries, each one bringing their own style, stories and history with love. So, come away with us to Africa! What you get: Learn about African weddings, culture, and expressions of love. 3-course meal demo Live music Recipes Storytelling The price is $75 per person.

{"name": "COLOR LAB NYC", "image": "", "description": "Color Lab NYC, with locations in Brooklyn and Manhattan, provides expert microblading, ombre brow and scalp micropigmentation services with a specialty in melanated skin.
Owned by a Black esthetician, Color Lab NYC has become a go-to for many NYC residents looking for someone who understands their skin’s unique attributes. Each client is provided with bespoke solutions that fit their brow and/or scalp needs..
Services:
Ombre brows is the process of creating beautiful semi-permanent brows using a specially crafted handheld tattoo pen and cosmetic pigment. The results yield a soft powder-like result (not your grandma’s old school brow tattoo!). This appointment is approximately 3 hours. Results can last from 12-24 months depending on skin type and lifestyle.
Microblading is the process of creating individual hair-like strokes in the brow using a special blade, handheld tool and cosmetic pigment. This appointment is approximately 2.5 hours. Microblading can last 12-18 months depending on skin type and lifestyle.
Scalp Micropigmentation is a new wave in scalp tattooing for both women and men! With the use of our pen shaped tattoo device, we create tiny dots of pigment on your scalp that resemble hair follicles. These tiny dots create the illusion of density for both thinning clients and those who are completely bald. We mean it! Edges, the crown of the head, the whole head…everything!
Appointment time is based on surface are we’r’e covering. {"name": "BLUE SKYES MASSAGE & WELLNESS CENTER", "image": "https://officialblackwallstreet.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/New-Client-Special-823x420.jpg", "description": "Our mission is to customize integrated therapeutic treatment sessions with clients who want to achieve a natural, safe, and noninvasive approach to holistic healing, by promoting and supporting the body’s innate natural ability to do so.

{"name": "BACK & BEYOND CHIROPRACTIC", "image": "", "description": "At Back & Beyond Chiropractic, we take great pride in providing the finest chiropractic care to each and every patient. We have included information below about the different chiropractic services offered in our Chandler chiropractic office, but please call us at 480-750-8900 if you have any questions!
Chiropractic Care
We provide spinal correction utilizing “state of the art” chiropractic techniques. Never in the history of chiropractic have we been able to provide the level of help and expertise that now exists. These newer correction methods are even safer, more comfortable and more effective than ever before. As a Doctor of Chiropractic, Dr. Dean has years of training and experience in spinal adjustment.Corrective Exercises.
Functional Medicine Modalities and Therapeutic Procedures
We teach our patients special “blueprint” exercises to help strengthen and correct their own unique problem. These exercises can be performed in the comfort of your own home and can improve the effectiveness of your spinal correction. In addition to skeletal misalignment, muscles and connective tissues can be out of place or strained by improper alignment and use. Specific exercises and stretches can help your body stay in balance and in health. Ensure your body is functioning at its peak with functional medicine modalities and therapeutic procedures. Often we don’t know we’re out of alignment, so we recommend you stop in for an initial spine exam to assess your current situation. Our main goal is to balance body structure and function. Our time-tested results provide optimal performance. It may not be a surprise, but re-aligning the body also results in greater well-being. In our functional medicine modalities and therapeutic procedures we often use orthotics and core stabilization. We focus on:
• Active Rehab Stretching
• Mobility Work
• Range of Motion
• Strengthening
• Posture Correction
Personal Training
Lose weight, improve fitness, or train for a physical activity and feel great. We offer one-on-one and group training for individual needs. Whether you’re looking to lose a few pounds or have a specific reason for training, we can help. With our specialization in sports health sciences, we give you the tools to improve your fitness for your entire life, and we teach you how to take care of yourself along the way.
Lifestyle Advice
Many of our patients come to see our chiropractor to address a specific pain symptom such as back pain, neck pain or headaches. While our chiropractor will address each patient’s specific condition with chiropractic care, we often find it helpful to “coach” our patients towards achieving a healthier lifestyle. For example, there may be certain activities that you should avoid or do differently to prevent yourself from unintentionally aggravating your particular health challenges. The goal of including lifestyle advice with a chiropractic care plan is to help each and every patient achieve the fulfilling and happy lifestyle they deserve, one that is full of the activities that are enjoyed most. We recognize that every single one of our patients is a whole person, and we use our expertise to help them reach total health and wellness
.
Nutritional Coaching
What does nutrition have to do with chiropractic care? The goal of chiropractic care is to help patients achieve total health and balance with their body, and as part of that goal we provide specific recommendations on nutritional supplements and healthy food choices. Nutritional counseling by our experienced chiropractic health professionals can assist a patient on their return to optimal health. Do you know which supplements and vitamins are good for you? Do you know how these supplements and vitamins interact with one another? At our Chandler chiropractic clinic, we can provide each patient with a structured nutritional program that is based on their individual needs.
Spinal & Postural Screenings
There is a saying that an ounce of prevention is worth a pound of cure. Your spinal health is no exception. Posture and spinal screenings by a trained and experienced chiropractor such as Dr. Dean Burchenson can help reveal important health information, unlocking the door to improved health and well-being. In order to help the community, we provide screenings at area malls, community events, health fairs and places of employment. Contact us today at 480-750-8900 to arrange a screening at your event or workplace.", "categories": ["back pain", " Carpel Tennel", " Chiropractic", " Choulder Pain", " Corrective chiropractic", " Headaches", " Knee Pain", " mobility issues", " Neck Pain", " Nutritional coaching", " Sport injuries", " Strength coaching", " therapy"], "contact": [{"type": "address", "value": "1655 W Chandler Blvd #4 Chandler, AZ 85224"}, {"type": "phone", "value": "(480) 750-8900"}, {"type": "e-mail", "value": "drdean@backandbeyondchiropractic.com"}, {"type": "website", "value": "www.backandbeyondchiropractic.com"}, {"type": "category", "value": "Health & Wellness, Therapy"}, {"type": "location", "value": "Arizona, Chandler"}], "hours": [{"day": "Mon", "hours": "07:30-18:00"}, {"day": "Tues", "hours": "07:30-18:00"}, {"day": "Wed", "hours": "07:30-18:30"}, {"day": "Thurs", "hours": "07:30-18:00"}]}

{"name": "COMFORT ZONE SECURITY, PROTECTION & INVESTIGATIONS, LLC", "image": "", "description": "Please allow me to briefly introduce my company. My name is Thomas “Mitch” Mitchell. The company is a minority and veteran owned business.
As the owner of the company I possess over 25 years of experience in security, protection and investigations. I served a total of 13 years in three different branches of the military. I am a former Memphis Police Detective, Former Federal Air Marshal and currently a reserve Lieutenant on the Moscow Mills Police Department. Top Rated Specialist in intelligence based executive protection High and Low profile operations. I am a Licensed by the State of Missouri as a PRIVATE INVESTIGATOR.
“An ounce of prevention saves a pound of cure.” Benjamin Franklin
Mr. Mitchell has worked in all aspects of the security field including Executive Protection, Celebrity Protection, High Profile operations, Low Profile operations, Venue, Concerts, Events, Press Junkets, Premier Red Carpets and Residential security. Mr. Mitchell has worked as a Solo Bodyguard for both “A” list Entertainment Professionals and Fortune 500 Executives. Mr. Mitchell specializes in armed and unarmed low profile operations. Some of the other services that our company offers are executive / dignitary protection and security for the clients and their family members. We provide protection and security to and from venues, at arrivals and departures; temporary and permanent residences; public places, social gatherings and family vacations. We also travel with clients aboard airlines to and from engagements.
Comfort Zone Security is available 24 / 7; we are on call around the clock to provide exceptional service and to take care of any emergency situations. We deploy licensed trained security agents to conduct hourly foot patrols, alarm responses, personal bodyguards, and mobile patrols. We also have an agreement with the local city and county police and sheriff departments that allow us to alert them in any major events garnering a response from them in a matter of a few minutes; feel free to review our website at your leisure at www.comfortzsecurity.com for a more in depth illustration of our services and credentials.
.
Thomas “Mitch” Mitchell
CEO / President
Comfort Zone Security, Protection & Investigations, LLC

{"name": "JORDAN EXECUTIVE TRAVEL SERVICE", "image": "", "description": "Jordan Executive Travel Service is a group of passionate travel professionals who believe that every destination has a heartbeat. Having a heart for solo travelers, several times a year we create small group travel experiences for like-minded travelers who are really explorers at heart. It’s an immersive experience in some of the world’s most amazing destinations that turns complete strangers into life long friends.
Even cruise vacations can be an indulgence with us. From private shore excursions to your own car and driver waiting for you in port. It’s just one of the many ways we can enhance your travel experience.

{"name": "HEALTH CARE TRAVELS", "image": "", "description": "Health Care Travels, LLC was established to solve the challenges faced by travel healthcare professionals in securing affordable short-term housing. We are a specialized website providing a centralized platform to help travel healthcare professionals find affordable and reliable short-term housing. Property owners can list properties they wish to rent to healthcare professionals on a work assignment. Healthcare travelers can locate short-term housing needs, pay for reservations securely online, and also request a roommate, become a scout or request scout services for unverified listings. Travelers are also able to list their properties for rent while they are away on an assignment.
Our Goal
To be the “Go To site” for ALL healthcare travelers housing needs.
Our Mission
We aim to help alleviate the stress of finding trusted, reliable, safe, and cost-efficient short­-term housing for traveling healthcare professionals while on assignments across the United States.
Health Care Travels
Health Care Travels, LLC was established in October 2017. It is a centralized website which serves as a meeting point for travel healthcare professionals on a work assignment in search of short-term housing and property owners who have a rental space.
As a property owner, you can list your short-term housing options after creating an account on our secure website. Healthcare professionals will have the ability to search through our website by city and state to locate housing where they may accept their next travel assignment. We will offer tools for direct communication between travelers and property owners so they can determine in the listed housing option is suitable for their needs.
If you are a traveler who wants to reduce the cost of housing, we also provide assistance in helping find roommates to help you achieve this without stress.
We are dedicated to providing a one-stop-shop platform that caters to every housing need for travel healthcare professionals. Additionally, our platform also allows travel healthcare professionals to make money from their properties by listing it on our website for the use of other healthcare travelers while they are away.
What More?
Health Care Travels also will provide a list of RV camping websites and resources that are affordable and recommended to healthcare travelers traveling by RV. We look forward to providing services globally; we open the door to working with professional healthcare travelers, property owners, and agencies as we continue to grow. Health Care Travels focuses on value and trust, and we believe that all users can get the best results as long as we provide the appropriate resources in one centralized location.
Meet Us
Our team fully understands that assignments can get canceled at any given moment, so Health Care Travels functions to negotiate suitable cancellation policies that are fair to Travelers and property owners. The founder and CEO of Health Care Travels advocates for affordable housing and leads the team to understanding the industry and its needs.
With our services, we bring more value to property owners that list on our robust platform by taking care and respecting homeowners listings. We alleviate the stress and length of time travelers search for housing options.
Sign up with us today and fully capitalize on the alternative housing trend for healthcare travelers! {"name": "REDS GROOMED MAN", "image": "", "description": "Red’s Groomed Man is a hair grooming brand for men of color headquartered in Philadelphia. The Founder and CEO created Red’s Groomed Man in her kitchen. She wanted to focus on the hair care of men by offering a range of products such as beard therapy oil, shampoo bar, the infamous beard treatment bar, and wave grease.
In the beginning, it was simply an experiment. It began with testing various fragrances and essential oils, just to see the results. While experimenting the focus remained on one thing — “creating products that would change the way men groom their hair today.” The creative journey started as a hobby, while the founder ran a full-time boutique marketing firm, but after sample testing the products with friends and family, she decided to launch her first round of a long list of hair grooming products for men.

Reds Groomed Man was first launched at its flagship location, Reds Creative Kutz, located at 1611 E. Wadsworth Ave Philadelphia, Pa. Reds Creative Kutz has been a staple in the community for more than 2 decades. The owner and master barber, Keith Gee played an intricate role in the development of each product, lending his decades of experience with men’s grooming to help develop a line of premium grooming products for men.

{"name": "COMPASS CONSULTING SERVICES, LLC", "image": "", "description": "Compass Consulting Services, LLC was established in Ohio in August of 2008 by co-founders, Tameka L. Taylor, Ph.D. and Ruth E. Ramos Clifford. In July 2013, Ruth Ramos Clifford stepped down as one of the partners. At that point, Tameka L. Taylor took over as the President of Compass Consulting Services, LLC. The owner and consultants of Compass have over 80 years of experience in designing and delivering diversity and leadership programs to organizations. They are experts in engaging participants in difficult but honest conversations around respect and inclusion in the workplace in a non-threatening manner where participants gain awareness and skills. Since 2008, Compass Consulting Services, LLC has remained in Ohio but has done work in other parts of the country including Iowa, Indiana, Washington, Michigan, Florida, North Carolina, Minnesota and Nebraska.
Compass Consulting Services, LLC is a certified minority and women-owned organizational development firm that helps companies meet their optimal performance by maximizing employee relationships and fostering inclusive work environments. We are experts in the following areas: Diversity (i.e. race, gender, socioeconomics, sexual orientation, generational differences, geography, etc.), Equity & Inclusion Management; Conflict Management; Communication; Leadership Development; and Team Building. We do this by offering the following services in: Training and Development; Diversity Audits/Organizational Assessments; Executive Coaching; Strategic Planning; Facilitation; Focus Groups; Equal Employment Opportunity Investigations; Equal Employment Opportunity (EEO) Regulations Training; and Anti-harassment and Ethics Training.
Compass Consulting Services, LLC was awarded a “Cuyahoga Metropolitan Housing Authority (CMHA) 2014 Community Partner Award.” In 2010 the company owners were awarded the 2010 Northeast Ohio Hispanic Chamber of Commerce “Entrepreneurs of the Year” Award, as well as the 2010 “President’s Award” by the Northern Ohio Minority Supplier Development Council.
Since their establishment, Compass Consulting Services, LLC has served over 425 clients, many of whom have been clients since 2008. We work in a variety of public, governmental, educational, manufacturing, law, financial, and non-profit organizations on projects ranging from an half-day training session to multi-level, multi-year, projects. Typically, we work with organizations that have up to 5,000 employees. We have worked with teams as small as three members to larger groups of 175 members at one time. We work with adults and youth and have the skill set to work at all levels of a system – individual, group, and organizational. {"name": "NATURAL ASH BODY", "image": "https://officialblackwallstreet.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/butter-mixed-2-copy.jpg", "description": "OUR PRODUCTS
Natural Ash is created and formulated by our founder, Ashley Cummings, RN. Each batch of body butter is handmade in Harlem with only natural ingredients. We understand that everyone’s skin is different and requires individual attention, therefore we have a variety of body butters.
OUR STORY
Working as an Oncology Registered Nurse and learning about the chemicals found in beauty products that can lead to cancer, I started to pay attention to the ingredients in my skincare products. As a result, I started to experiment with natural body butters sourced from Africa, as well as different oils. I wanted to know what I was putting on my skin for hydration, as the product will then go into my body.
As a nurse, I naturally want those around me to take care of their bodies and skin. After all, your skin’s health is a direct reflection of your overall health and wellness. This is your body’s largest organ and its protectant. Healthy skin gives people self-esteem and the confidence to reach their highest potential.
The name, Natural Ash means to naturally rid your skin of being “ashy”. Natural Ash embodies health, skincare, and positivity. Taking care of your skin gives you self esteem and a positive self-image. Natural Ash not only takes care of your skin but also is environmentally conscious when selecting ingredients and packaging. Remember, always Care Beneath Your Skin.
OUR FOUNDER
Ashley is a Registered Nurse originally from Massachusetts but has been living in New York City since 2009. She began making body butters in her Harlem apartment in 2017. As a Registered Nurse, Ashley knows the importance of skincare and ensuring that harmful chemicals are not a part of your daily skincare regimen.", "categories": ["body care", " chemotherapy", " dry skin", " eczema", " healthyskin", " naturalproducts", " No Chemicals", " nontoxicproduct", " nontoxicproducts", " psoriasis", " skin care", " skincareroutine", " total body care"], "contact": [{"type": "address", "value": "New York, NY"}, {"type": "e-mail", "value": "ashley@naturalashbody.com"}, {"type": "website", "value": "naturalashbody.com"}, {"type": "category", "value": "Health & Wellness, Podiatry, Skin Care Products"}, {"type": "location", "value": "New Hampshire, New York, Online-Based, Web-Based"}], "hours": [{"day": "Mon", "hours": "10-8"}, {"day": "Tues", "hours": "10-8"}, {"day": "Wed", "hours": "10-8"}, {"day": "Thurs", "hours": "10-8"}, {"day": "Fri", "hours": "10-8"}, {"day": "Sat", "hours": "10-8"}, {"day": "Sun", "hours": "10-8"}]}

Some may ask what where did the brand name come from…brought to you by one believer. It’s simple – in Christ, we’re all ONE body. So these are simple messages brought to us via His Spirit. “God’s divine power has given us everything we need for life and for godliness. This power was given to us through knowledge of the one who called us by his own glory and integrity.”
— II PETER 1:3
Philosophy
Brought to You by One Believer (aka B2Yb1B) is an urban Christian brand that boldly expresses the simplicity of our Faith. Each design is based on scripture that assists us as we maneuver through our daily lives.
The brand’s designs are unique. They are not meant to be perfect or “crisp” as other designs are presented. With subtle hints of imperfection, the designs are meant to bring clarity. We are being perfected on this life’s journey. Life is forever transitioning. With our marching orders “walk by faith and not by sight”, each design is created. This makes life so much more fun…just seeing His perfection in the imperfect person, situation, or these designs.
